items.title: Three weeks after acquiring Windsurf, Cognition offers staff the exit door
items.description: Cognition is also laying off 30 employees. Those who take the buyout are expected to work 80+ hour weeks.

items.title: ElevenLabs launches an AI music generator, which it claims is cleared for commercial use
items.description: The AI audio-generation unicorn ElevenLabs announced the launch of a new model that allows users to generate music that's cleared for commercial use.

items.title: Trump says he’ll announce semiconductor and chip tariffs
items.description: This announcement comes as the Trump administration is also mulling over its approach to AI chip export restrictions.

items.title: Hacker used a voice phishing attack to steal Cisco customers’ personal information
items.description: Cisco disclosed a data breach including customer names, organization names, addresses, email addresses, and phone numbers of Cisco.com users.
